Title: Create commands to say to smart homes
Description: Create a command that you would say to tell a smart home whether the lights should be on or off.
Keywords: text, creative, research, academic, writing, smart home, internet of things, artificial intelligence
Answer.WritingTexts: When I go to step into a room please turn the lights on.
